[% META title = 'Frequently Asked Questions' %]

<div class="documentation-page">
    <div class="doc-header">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>
        
        <div class="doc-meta">
            <span class="updated">Last Updated: May 31, 2024</span>
            <span class="author">Author: Support Team</span>
            <span class="status">Status: Active</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
        <h2>General Questions</h2>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What is Comserv?</h3>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Comserv is a comprehensive web application platform designed to manage various aspects of community services, 
                including site management, user administration, and specialized modules for different industries.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I report a bug or request a feature?</h3>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>You can report bugs or request features by:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Contacting your site administrator</li>
                    <li>Using the Help Desk feature if enabled on your site</li>
                    <li>Submitting a ticket through the support system</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What browsers are supported?</h3>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Comserv supports all modern browsers, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Google Chrome (recommended)</li>
                    <li>Mozilla Firefox</li>
                    <li>Microsoft Edge</li>
                    <li>Safari</li>
                </ul>
                <p>For the best experience, please keep your browser updated to the latest version.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
        <h2>Account Management</h2>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I reset my password?</h3>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>To reset your password:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click on the "Login" link</li>
                    <li>Click "Forgot Password"</li>
                    <li>Enter your email address</li>
                    <li>Follow the instructions in the password reset email</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can I change my username?</h3>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Usernames cannot be changed directly by users. If you need to change your username, please contact your site administrator.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What should I do if I'm locked out of my account?</h3>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>If you're locked out of your account:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Try the password reset procedure first</li>
                    <li>If that doesn't work, contact your site administrator</li>
                    <li>Provide your username and the email address associated with your account</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-section">
        <h2>Technical Issues</h2>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>The site is loading slowly. What can I do?</h3>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>If the site is loading slowly, try these steps:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Clear your browser cache and cookies</li>
                    <li>Check your internet connection</li>
                    <li>Try using a different browser</li>
                    <li>If the problem persists, contact support</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>I'm seeing error messages. What should I do?</h3>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>If you encounter error messages:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Take a screenshot of the error</li>
                    <li>Note what you were doing when the error occurred</li>
                    <li>Report the issue to your administrator with these details</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
